                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="85606" author="jlevi" created="Tue, 3 Jun 2014 15:52:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patches landed to Master. Remaining work is being tracked under &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4423&quot; title=&quot;Tracking of patches from upstream kernel to Lustre client&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4423&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4423&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="84568" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 21 May 2014 00:47:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All patches for this ticket have been merged. Can we close this ticket and move all further work under &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4423&quot; title=&quot;Tracking of patches from upstream kernel to Lustre client&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4423&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4423&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="82915" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 30 Apr 2014 20:28:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This ticket and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4423&quot; title=&quot;Tracking of patches from upstream kernel to Lustre client&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4423&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4423&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; appear to be the same. Depending on which one is marked as a duplicate we need to make it a subtask of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4416&quot; title=&quot;support for 3.12 linux kernel&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4416&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4416&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="76788" author="bogl" created="Tue, 11 Feb 2014 22:40:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;some upstream mods listed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4416&quot; title=&quot;support for 3.12 linux kernel&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4416&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4416&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="76787" author="jhammond" created="Tue, 11 Feb 2014 22:32:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are tons but most of them are typo fixes and further cleanup. See &lt;a href=&quot;https://git.kernel.org/cgit/linux/kernel/git/gregkh/staging.git/log/drivers/staging/lustre&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git.kernel.org/cgit/linux/kernel/git/gregkh/staging.git/log/drivers/staging/lustre&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think Oleg has an issue for this already.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="76786" author="jay" created="Tue, 11 Feb 2014 22:30:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the first patch is at: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/9230&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/9230&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and upstream kernel patch is at: &lt;a href=&quot;http://marc.info/?l=linux-fsdevel&amp;amp;m=139215000101035&amp;amp;w=2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://marc.info/?l=linux-fsdevel&amp;amp;m=139215000101035&amp;amp;w=2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
